downloadTitle: BizTalk Server Accelerator for SWIFT - Message Pack 2015 CU2
downloadDescription: Cumulative Update 2 for BizTalk A4Swift Message Pack 2015
detailsSection: This cumulative update contains hotfixes for issues that were resolved after the final, production release of Microsoft BizTalk Accelerator for SWIFT Message Pack 2015.
systemRequirementsSection: Windows 7, Windows Server 2008 R2, Windows 8, Windows Server 2012, Windows 8.1, Windows Server 2012 R2
installInstructionSection:
The Microsoft BizTalk Accelerator for SWIFT Message Pack 2015 should be downloaded and installed successfully before installing this Cumulative Update.

Download the self-extracting archive, then execute it to extract the setup program to a temporary directory. From the temporary location, execute the setup.exe program, which will install the update.
